@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Create profile
POST {{baseUrl}}/profiles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "programming",
  "allowedCategories": ["code", "software"],
  "blockedCategories": ["violence"],
  "createdBy": "admin",
  "creatorEmail": "admin@test.com"
}

### Get all profiles
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles

### Get profile by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/profiles/REPLACE_WITH_ID

### Delete profile
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/profiles/REPLACE_WITH_ID